1.m_mText:
"Vampires are heretics, followers of the demons of chaos, vassals of Dracula, and the source of the sins of the last judgment.
They must all be eradicated, purified by the Church.
Those born with white hair are vampires;
Those born with red eyes are vampires;
Those who claim to have memories from a past life are vampires;
Those who would conduct sorcery against the Church are vampires;
Those who transform under the blood moon are vampires;
...
Witch Hunters will earn Aeon's blessing based on the number of vampires they have slain.
Purge the sins caused by those who stray from the path and become part of the exalted and eternal.
Better to kill an innocent than to allow a vampire to escape judgment."

2.m_mText:
"Vampires can be identified by four physical features: White skin, pointed ears, sharp molars, and blood sigils.
They feed on human blood to sustain their bloodless forms;
their ears are tools for capturing living beings;
their teeth are daggers for piercing human skin;
and their sigils support their deceitful appearances.
If identification is uncertain, use holy fire.
Holy fire shall reveal the truth hidden beneath the blood sigils.
Bind them to a cross and ignite the holy fire with kindling. If they emit a piercing wail and their bones do not melt after the flames die out, you may confirm their identity as a vampire."
